  "title": "(ADT) 💰LONG TERM SALES SUPPORT NEEDED💰 / Up to 4k basic",
  "description": "<p>💰LONG TERM SALES SUPPORT NEEDED💰</p><p></p><p>📍 Location: Near Jurong East</p><p>⏰ Working Hours: Mon to Fri, 9am till 6:30pm (OT needed when required)</p><p>💰 Salary: Up to $4000</p><p></p><p>✨AN ADVANTAGE IF HAVE FREIGHT FORWARDING EXPERIENCE✨</p><p></p><p>📝Jobscope</p><p>👉🏻Provide dedicated support for CargoWise (CW) ensuring accuracy and compliance with company processes</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Act as the subject matter expert for sales teams on CW sales module queries and correct data setup.</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Data validation and basic analysis on sales entries to identify discrepancies and prevent billing issues.</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Ensure clear/smooth implementation of Client rates with Customer Quotation.</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Support and participate in CargoWise implementation and post-implementation phases</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Preparation of sales / shipments reports.</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Develop, review, and maintain Standard Operating Procedures.</p><p></p><p>👉🏻 Work with Accounts, Sales, and Operations teams.</p><p></p><p>Applicants who are interested, pls email to recruit@onehirestaffing.com or call 6031 4933</p><p>1. Full Name</p><p>2. Residential Location</p><p>3. Start/End Date</p><p></p><p>R1104563 (Tan Si Ni Shirley Gwen)</p><p>EA License: 25C3058 (One Hire Staffing Pte Ltd)</p>",
